OL,5, A Fujitsu manager called a Post Office 
OL,6, sub-postmaster a "nasty chap" ahead of 
OL,7, a legal battle that left him bankrupt, 
OL,8, an inquiry has heard.                  
OL,10,FPeter Sewell, who was part of the Post 
OL,11,FOffice Account Security Team at the    
OL,12,Fcompany, made the comment about Lee    
OL,13,FCastleton in an email in 2006.         
OL,15,FMr Castleton was found to have a       
OL,16,F#25,000 shortfall at his branch after  
OL,17,Fbeing sued by the Post Office.         
OL,19,FMr Sewell told the inquiry: "I don't   
OL,20,Fknow why that was written."            
